\id 1TI - Abureni
\h 1 A̠timoti
\toc3 1 A̠tim
\toc2 1 A̠timoti
\toc1 O̠pu̠r A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m A̠timoti Bho̠
\mt2 O̠pu̠r A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m
\mt1 A̠timoti
\mt2 Bho̠
\imt1 Otighom
\ip A̠timoti aro̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ i̠b̠aragu̠ma wa̠ a̠tua̠n Apo̠l ibom bho̠. Ka̠din A̠timoti aro̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ aso̠si̠ E̠fi̠so̠s ma̠ odi obhel, sa̠ Apo̠l a̠ruom i̠na ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠marame̠ni̠ i̠karabh atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ (1 A̠tim 3:4). Apo̠l a̠b̠em ologi ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ ozua̠n A̠timoti (A̠tim 3:14, 15; 4:13), ya̠a̠, i̠na a̠d̠ia̠ age̠ ma̠ a̠lebh onon agi̠o̠m A̠timoti, ma̠ onigha̠ a̠ga̠i a̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ogir aso̠si̠ bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ologi ta̠ A̠timoti, na̠ okikiom o̠yo̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ okubh we̠mu̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠. Apo̠l a̠b̠eton ekpo abar abar i̠se̠ a̠bhin a̠kikiom A̠timoti. I̠na ab̠aram na̠ a̠ga̠i i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ irileghom aso̠si̠, na̠ d̠a̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n i̠ko̠l ologhom, b̠o̠ka̠ a̠bhin i̠nye̠ amarame̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igunugha̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ orugha̠n a̠d̠ien kere kere rebu a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠. A̠lebh onon agu̠b̠an ola̠ ulebh u̠gi̠o̠m A̠timoti ku̠ku̠m, ya̠a̠ a̠d̠izo ikikiom bho̠ od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ na̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ irileghom raso̠si̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ a̠didon. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, a̠lebh d̠o̠yo̠ onon bha̠ o̠gbara a̠d̠ire ola̠ obhin orileghom, na̠ ola̠ obhin osibhom i̠to̠to̠gi̠ aso̠si̠.
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠
\io1 Otighom \ior (1:1-20)\ior*
\io1 I̠ghaghana ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igunugha̠ \ior (2:1-15)\ior*
\io1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠siseiny na̠ i̠ko̠l \ior (3:1-16)\ior*
\io1 I̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ odoni ikei na̠ ogbo i̠to̠to̠gi̠ \ior (4:1—5:25)\ior*
\io1 Re̠kal a̠kikiom na̠ ogir bho̠ \ior (6:1-21)\ior*
\io1 Ogir ologhom Akrai̠st na̠ i̠ghaghana wa̠ Apo̠l aghaghana ma̠ A̠timoti bho̠.
\c 1
\s1 Ibheleguma̠
\p 
\v 1 A̠lebh onon ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ Apo̠l, o̠ni̠ogir ta̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s a̠ru, d̠a̠ i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar, na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s wa̠ eb̠em ologi d̠i̠yar bho̠,
\v 2 ma̠ onigha̠ oyom A̠timoti, a̠ga̠i o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠. E̠ne̠ghe̠, okpon igbirigbir, na̠ ekima̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar bho̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ anwa.
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igunugha̠
\p 
\v 3 Agu̠o̠ ami̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi d̠oyom ma̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ E̠fi̠so̠s, igiel bho̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠ten na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Ame̠sidonia̠ bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ aghaghana ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igunugha̠ bho̠ ma̠ o̠we̠le̠man ogir o̠ku̠a.
\v 4 Gba ma̠a̠, awa e̠we̠le̠man rasu̠gbagba ezin o̠to̠ na̠ id̠udul ibom ro̠we̠de̠ d̠awa ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠ro̠d̠o̠ bho̠, ya̠ na̠ emutiom raku̠anan ku̠ku̠m, ya̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ enigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ orugh a̠ghud̠um ologi ima̠ra̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 5 Ezin abar wa̠ u̠tu̠n u̠to̠ ma̠ i̠to̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠ bha̠, od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ odi ta̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ ologi e̠b̠ab̠ala, na̠ ob̠eb̠i eloghoma̠n, na̠ a̠ga̠i ologi ima̠ra̠ a̠tula̠n odi.
\v 6 Idi ogbo na̠ e̠baro̠n e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n e̠gi̠ ka̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ ibhelebhel a̠fugh.
\v 7 Awa na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh oten i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ awa na̠ efugh, na̠ ezin asu̠gbagba ya̠ awa na̠ ebhin alu̠kpo̠ ologi na̠ e̠gba bho̠.
\v 8 I̠yar ologhom ma̠a̠ oloko bho̠ a̠bhon, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ orughom agu̠o̠ a̠soran bho̠.
\v 9 I̠yar ologhom nyen ma̠a̠, udin d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ erugh ya̠ igielake̠ omutiom oloko bho̠, ya̠a̠ udin isorogi ma̠ ro̠kpe̠, na̠ iwia̠n ma̠ ra̠dila̠de irileghom, na̠ ighel ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ idighi ma̠ i̠karabh, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh ado̠l i̠te̠i̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ orugh d̠o̠ ma̠ ado̠l igielake̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ abar ola̠ ima̠ra̠ o̠ro̠d̠o̠, na̠ i̠ze̠ ma̠ ronweni na̠ ro̠we̠de̠, na̠ i̠ze̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom,
\v 10 na̠ id̠eme̠ma, na̠ ilobhiri ya̠ na̠ ekod̠uom ilobhiri, na̠ anwani̠ ya̠ na̠ ekod̠uom anwani̠, na̠ ib̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom, na̠ i̠gba ma̠ igunugha̠, na̠ ronyob̠a̠ igunugha̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ewia̠n a̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠,
\v 11 ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Itutumeni iru, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton alo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠.
\s1 E̠ne̠ghe̠ wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Apo̠l bho̠
\p 
\v 12 Ami̠ na̠ ase̠bh Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar, wa̠ abi̠gh ma̠ ami̠ akpe̠ sa̠ aso̠n ami̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ ogir o̠yo̠ bho̠.
\v 13 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten, ami̠ ifugh gha̠n a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ i̠na, sa̠ ami̠ igbikimeni ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ami̠ i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠kpon ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir agu̠o̠ ami̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠gir i̠karabh bho̠, ezin bho̠ ami̠ ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ i̠na.
\v 14 Sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar a̠bhin d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ na̠ etula̠n, ya̠ i̠wo̠l d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s iru bho̠.
\v 15 Onon a̠ga̠i o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ola̠ akpe̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠da obhin, ma̠a̠: “Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s a̠ru ma̠ i̠se̠n e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ otenemeni id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.” Sa̠ ami̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh wa̠ igurom ipu bho̠.
\v 16 Ya̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠kpon ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s ta̠ a̠rughom ami̠ a̠guri ma̠ agu̠o̠ elegh a̠ma̠ne d̠o̠yo̠, eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ ami̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh wa̠ a̠gurom a̠pu bho̠ eka̠. Obha̠ na̠ a̠leriom agu̠o̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ e̠ro̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠, d̠a̠ o̠gu̠man, sa̠ ta̠ ema̠ra̠ i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul bho̠.
\v 17 I̠se̠n bha̠, edim na̠ isosorogia̠n e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ O̠li̠le̠ma wa̠ ka̠ kid̠ud̠ul bho̠, wa̠ omugh d̠o̠ bho̠, wa̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien bho̠, wa̠ i̠na ku̠ku̠m aro̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ga̠i bho̠, tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul. Aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a.
\v 18 O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ A̠timoti, ami̠ na̠ ato̠ ma̠ i̠to̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠ omuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ ya̠ uwa̠ ugboloma̠ nyam d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten bho̠, bo̠ka̠ igiel anwa i̠ru̠ru̠an, anwa amar a̠we ma̠ e̠gham bho̠.
\v 19 Sibhe ma̠ eloghoma̠n d̠oyom ma̠ akparame̠ni̠, ma̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ologi e̠b̠ab̠ala. Idi ogbo ighel i̠ye̠, sa̠ i̠we̠le̠man o̠nagha iya̠ ologi na̠ agba. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa.
\v 20 Ahi̠me̠ni̠o̠s na̠ Ale̠kzanda bha̠ idi ogbo ya̠ na̠ egir o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin. Ami̠ na̠ a̠b̠eton awa alo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ Eru bho̠ ma̠ ogbikimeni, b̠o̠ka̠ awa e̠we̠le̠man a̠fugh i̠basi̠ ogboloma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\c 2
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ osiseiny a̠siseiny
\p 
\v 1 O̠pu̠r abar bho̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠kikiom inyin ma̠a̠, ipuru ma̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh bho̠, ma̠ esiseiny, ma̠ e̠mara ma̠ eni, ma̠ e̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ egboloma̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠.
\v 2 Isiseinye ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ Aru̠li̠le̠ma na̠ ipa̠n ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠yar orugh a̠ghud̠um eb̠okum na̠ ekima̠, na̠ oghila̠n A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ orugh a̠ghud̠um edim.
\v 3 Osiseiny o̠ko̠no̠n a̠bhon, sa̠ a̠d̠igh ologi ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar,
\v 4 wa̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ oten na̠ ologhom a̠ga̠i a̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 5 Ezin bho̠ onin A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ onin o̠mara ma̠ enie ku̠ku̠m od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom na̠ A̠zib̠a̠. I̠na Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s,
\v 6 wa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ obhin o̠ta eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh ola̠ umutiom d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ u̠to̠ bho̠.
\v 7 Obha̠ ezin bho̠ u̠so̠n ami̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠-ogir na̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi na̠ a̠ga̠i onigha̠ Ibhebhia̠n bho̠. Ami̠ na̠ agba ma̠ ya̠gia̠ga̠i, igunugha̠ d̠o̠.
\v 8 Ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh agu̠o̠ ola̠ kesi kesi ilobhiri a̠nwunom na̠ esiseiny a̠siseiny, awa eb̠egion aru̠gu̠o̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala e̠gi̠o̠m anyu̠, aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ awa ko ogurumia̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ rologi, bo̠d̠o̠ ko o̠ku̠anan d̠o̠ ma̠ aku̠anan.
\v 9 Ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh nyen agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwani̠ ta̠ e̠mar ebura̠ ma̠ ibura̠ ya̠ awa ta̠ ed̠igh edim o̠bi̠gh. Awa oguri d̠o̠ ma̠ asi̠ghal d̠awa ma̠ ya̠ ipe ya̠ osorogi adi̠e̠l, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠ke̠le̠gi̠an a̠goli, na̠ i̠ge̠, na̠ i̠ku̠ta, na̠ i̠b̠o̠lo̠, ya̠ ubhin a̠gol bo̠d̠o̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ e̠mu̠ u̠le̠m, ya̠ ibom a̠b̠ua̠.
\v 10 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, bha̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ anwani̠ ya̠ na̠ egir ib̠eb̠i ya̠ izuzua̠n i̠re̠ma agu̠o̠ awa na̠ obuom A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.
\v 11 Ani̠ebhom aro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m atu̠ghan d̠a̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu.
\v 12 Ami̠ i̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ani̠ebhom ta̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ta̠ aragha ma̠ a̠limon a̠rileghom olobhiri o̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ aro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m.
\v 13 Iloghome ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠d̠ia̠ ale̠m Adam kisa̠ ale̠m Ivu.
\v 14 Adam d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ugelemeni bho̠, ya̠a̠ ani̠ebhom bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠gir i̠karabh.
\v 15 Aro̠ ku ma̠ o̠ku̠a eka̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ i̠mara, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na a̠bhin ologi ima̠ra̠, na̠ etula̠n, na̠ onyen ologi d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agi̠o̠m d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, d̠a̠ osibhom ozu.
\c 3
\s1 A̠ma̠rugh ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ ogbo irileghom d̠a̠ Aso̠si̠
\p 
\v 1 Onon a̠kikiom ola̠ a̠d̠igh esi, ma̠a̠: O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ ebhir oten o̠ni̠ irileghom aso̠si̠, bha̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh ob̠eb̠i ogir.
\v 2 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, e̠kal ali̠o̠m o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ irileghom, a̠bhin onin ani̠, a̠kimeni ma̠ ozu, ato̠to̠gi̠o̠m a̠ma̠rugh, ologhom abar, a̠d̠igh edim, ada ma̠ isuloma̠ a̠bhin na̠ onyen ologi, atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ na̠ e̠mar,
\v 3 o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠d̠amin, oponoma̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ okima̠kima̠ o̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠b̠e̠m d̠o̠, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ e̠d̠o̠gh okpoki.
\v 4 I̠na aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ amar na̠ a̠rileghom eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠, sa̠ na̠ erugh a̠ma̠rugh ozuruna̠ eghoi.
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ orileghom eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠, ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ a̠loghom agu̠o̠ okponom aso̠si̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 6 I̠na o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ororua̠ o̠ni̠-i̠tu̠o̠no̠m ta̠ Akrai̠st, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na na̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu a̠mel onin emel wa̠ udin usobh ase̠ ubhumeni ma̠ Eru bho̠.
\v 7 Ob̠eb̠i a̠ma̠rugh d̠o̠yo̠ agba i̠na a̠leriom a̠nwunom ya̠ o̠gi̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na na̠ omel a̠d̠igh ari̠ghe̠l, sekina̠ osor e̠te̠ i̠kpati̠ ta̠ eru bho̠.
\s1 A̠ma̠rugh ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ Ogbo I̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Aso̠si̠
\p 
\v 8 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ogbo i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠a̠ aso̠si̠, e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ erugh ado̠l ya̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠. Awa o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo igelemeni, bo̠d̠o̠ ro̠d̠a ma̠ a̠min, bo̠d̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh o̠te̠i̠ i̠karabh asu̠o̠.
\v 9 Awa ebhin e̠b̠ab̠ala eloghoma̠n esibhom ima̠ra̠ ologi ilologia̠n bho̠.
\v 10 O̠d̠a okpon a̠nwunom ya̠ o̠ku̠a, kisa̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ ogbo i̠to̠to̠gi̠ aso̠si̠ ku̠gba ma̠ e̠kal ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m bo̠.
\v 11 Anwani̠ d̠awa eka̠ erugh ado̠l ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ iya̠ ta̠ ozuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi, ogbo i̠me̠ghe̠nyan d̠o̠. Awa e̠ro̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekimeni ma̠ a̠ruzu, sa̠ na̠ ebhin d̠a̠ igielake̠ na̠ egir kabar kabar.
\v 12 O̠ni̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ onin ani̠, aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ amar na̠ erileghom anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 13 A̠nwunom ta̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠mar na̠ egir ogir d̠awa. Sa̠ awa ta̠ enwuna̠ ma̠ obom alu̠kpo̠ ologi d̠a̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠a̠ awa d̠a̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s.
\s1 Ezin A̠lebh ta̠ Apo̠l
\p 
\v 14 Agu̠o̠ ami̠ na̠ age̠ ma̠ a̠lebh onon na̠ a̠ruom anwa bho̠, bha̠ na̠ ebhir ami̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠r oru ra̠ ozua̠n oyom.
\v 15 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ ami̠ ibia̠ ma̠ oru, agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ a̠loghom agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom i̠kpe̠ ma̠ orugh d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ga̠i bho̠, wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ e̠ko̠ na̠ o̠de̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 16 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠mutiom a̠leriom i̠yar bho̠ obom ilologia̠n:
\q1 Akrai̠st a̠ru d̠a̠ ipulupul ozu,
\q2 sa̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba a̠mutiom ma̠a̠, i̠na amar a̠rugh d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,
\q1 sa̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠na,
\q2 sa̠ u̠gba i̠na umutiom d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom,
\q1 sa̠ a̠nwunom e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ ima̠ra̠ i̠na,
\q2 sa̠ ukpobh i̠na ubhuneni d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n.
\c 4
\s1 Ogbo Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ Igunugha̠
\p 
\v 1 E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ amar agba a̠mutiom ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ rekunuguma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, idi a̠nwunom ta̠ etiba̠ra̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ e̠nagha ma̠ aru̠mu̠gh igunugha̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ a̠ruru.
\v 2 Wa̠ ibhelebhel i̠gbamigunugha̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ eloghoma̠n bho̠ na̠ asa ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l awa bho̠.
\v 3 Awa ibhin ma̠ o̠walan ilom bha̠ e̠tu̠tu̠, sa̠ na̠ edin od̠e idi ra̠d̠ien ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ale̠m agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ bho̠ ta̠ e̠da ebhin na̠ ali̠se̠bh sa̠ ta̠ eleriom ya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 4 Kabar kabar A̠zib̠a̠ ale̠m, o̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠yar oghel d̠o̠ ma̠ odi abar i̠se̠, ya̠a̠ o̠da obhi̠n na̠ ali̠se̠bh.
\v 5 Ezin bho̠, o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠siseiny na̠ e̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.
\s1 Ob̠eb̠i Ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s
\p 
\v 6 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ anwa a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ma̠ a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, bha̠ anwa oten ob̠eb̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠, na̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ anwa ibhin onyen ologi i̠nagha bho̠, imuzo d̠a̠ ozu.
\v 7 Ya̠a̠, ko onwuna̠ ma̠ abar a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠karabh asu̠gbagba na̠ id̠ud̠ul ya̠ emirobh. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ tu̠ghane̠ ma̠ orugh a̠ghud̠um ola̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ itutumeni.
\v 8 Oselegi ma̠ ozu d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠, ya̠a̠ orugh a̠ma̠rugh oghila̠n A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal ya̠ ta̠ e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠. Isibhe ma̠ ogua̠n i̠se̠n oghud̠um onon na̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.
\v 9 Onon a̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ola̠ akpe̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠mar o̠da obhin.
\v 10 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠yar na̠ owia̠n na̠ ogir ibom, ezin bho̠ i̠yar na̠ obhin A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠ na̠ ob̠em ologi, i̠na bha̠ Witenemeni eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, okunukun ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ i̠na bho̠.
\v 11 Kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠nigha̠ awa, ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa nyen.
\v 12 Ko oma̠ra̠ ka̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠din agu̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ okubh o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠kpon anwa aki̠ri̠me̠ni̠. Ya̠a̠, rughe ma̠ ado̠l ya̠ ipa̠n ogbo ima̠ra̠ bho̠ ta̠ e̠ta, d̠a̠ a̠fugh o̠nu̠ na̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠oyom, d̠a̠ etula̠n d̠oyom, d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom, na̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala ologi d̠oyom.
\v 13 Kisa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠ru, bha̠ bhine gha̠n ma̠ obhel a̠sen A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n, kikiome, ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.
\v 14 Ko oghel enigha̠ e̠mu̠gh wa̠ od̠i na̠ anwa bho̠, wa̠ unigha̠ nyam igiel bho̠ ikei bho̠ i̠gbamagi̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa d̠a̠ ozu d̠oyom, iwa̠ igboloma̠ bho̠.
\v 15 Ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, bo̠ka̠ eloloma̠ ogir d̠oyom emite ma̠ ola̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ta̠ abi̠gh
\v 16 Mare̠ ma̠ a̠kpona̠ ma̠ od̠ighi i̠d̠i̠ar d̠oyom na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠oyom. Ro̠ ma̠ ogir ogir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, ezin bho̠, ka̠ anwa igir o̠ku̠a sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ozu d̠oyom na̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠nagha nyam bho̠.
\c 5
\s1 Agu̠o̠ obhin orugha̠n ogbo ya̠ // od̠i d̠a̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠
\p 
\v 1 Ko obhin i̠gam a̠kikiom ikei o̠ni̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠. Kikiome ma̠ ikubh-anwi̠i̠ny agu̠o̠ a̠rumor.
\v 2 Rugha̠ne ma̠ ikei a̠nwunom anwani̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ronweni, ikubh-anwi̠nyan ma̠ agu̠o̠ aru̠marani̠, d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ko o̠pi̠o̠gho̠m d̠o̠ awa d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal.
\v 3 Lo̠ghe̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ rekpukele anwani̠ ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ rekpukele anwani̠ ga̠i.
\v 4 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ ekpukele ani̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny bo̠d̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny igha̠la̠, bha̠ awa ekponom i̠na, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠kponom awa, sa̠ ogir o̠ku̠a a̠bhon d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, ekpukele ani̠ ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ ekpukele ani̠ ga̠i, ya̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠, bha̠ na̠ a̠bhin A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠b̠em ologi, sa̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠ma̠ne na̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠siseiny a̠siseiny a̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n, na̠ a̠puru i̠na ma̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠.
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, ekpukele ani̠ ola̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ e̠me̠me̠m e̠mara̠nwunom onon, bha̠ na̠ a̠mugh, aro̠ ku ma̠ i̠na od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um eka̠.
\v 7 Kikiome awa ma̠ ra̠kikiom i̠nye̠n b̠o̠ka̠ u̠bi̠gh abar e̠kal obhin o̠li̠o̠m awa.
\v 8 Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ okponom ogbo a̠ghisia̠n d̠o̠yo̠, okunukun a̠nwunom eghunotu d̠o̠yo̠, bha̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ aku̠a ma̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠ sa̠ a̠gurom a̠pu ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st.
\v 9 Ko o̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ekpukele ani̠ ma̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire rekpukele anwani̠ bho̠, a̠ten ola̠ o̠nu̠ ala bho̠ na̠ epel e̠rabharabh (60), ola̠ awal owolom d̠o̠yo̠ ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠ma.
\v 10 I̠na aro̠ ma̠ ani̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh edim d̠a̠ a̠misigh eb̠la̠ ogbo sa̠ u̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i ogir d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ amar a̠rughom anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ onyen ologi ola̠ o̠ki̠o̠gho̠m risuloma̠, na̠ otitologh a̠sike\x - \xo 5:10 \xt Azo̠n 13:1-17\x* a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ alo̠gh gha̠n agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ i̠kparama ado̠l, sa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ obhel a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ogir ib̠eb̠i.
\v 11 Ko o̠lo̠gh a̠rid̠ien rekpukele anwani̠ ya̠ od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ ikubh, i̠kparakpar rebhiroma̠ ozu d̠awa ta̠ epel iya̠ awa inwuna̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh omula̠ o̠wal ilom,
\v 12 sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ ebhum ase̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa osibh d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r ogua̠n awa bho̠.
\v 13 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, awa ta̠ eten i̠gbu̠o̠ro̠gbu̠o̠r, sa̠ ta̠ erugh rado̠l ya̠ o̠d̠u̠a otu oten otu. Ka̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠gbu̠o̠ro̠gbu̠o̠r ku̠ku̠m, ya̠a̠ ta̠ eten ogbo i̠me̠ghe̠nyan, na̠ ra̠d̠ikelekpum, efughogh i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠.
\v 14 Oku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠kikiom agu̠o̠ ola̠ ikubh rekpukele anwani̠ ta̠ emula̠ e̠wal ilom, e̠maragi̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny, ekponom a̠rutu d̠awa. Sa̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien bho̠ ko onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ezin ola̠ odin ofugh i̠karabh ogboloma̠ awa.
\v 15 I̠bi̠ghe̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n d̠a̠ idi awa na̠ e̠baro̠n e̠d̠u̠a na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m Eru bho̠.
\v 16 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, ani̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ogbo a̠ghisia̠n ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ rekpukele anwani̠, bha̠ i̠na alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠kponom awa. O̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠dol bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, b̠o̠ka̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ ekponom a̠ga̠i rekpukele anwani̠ ya̠ i̠kpe̠ bho̠.
\v 17 Ikei ya̠ na̠ e̠mar na̠ erileghom aso̠si̠ bho̠ e̠kpe̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ asu̠wo̠ i̠wal a̠bin, okunukun ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠kparame̠ni̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ na̠ e̠sasaragi̠, sekina̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠.
\v 18 Ezin bho̠, A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠,
\q1 “Ko o̠gho̠ro̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠kpegi ma̠ o̠nu̠ e̠nam ogir bho̠ ma̠ igiel i̠na na̠ aze̠re̠gi̠ na̠ akagi̠o̠n ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠.”\x - \xo 5:18 \xt Oloko 25:4\x* Opa̠n esi eka̠ sa̠ agba ma̠a̠,
\q1 “O̠ni̠ ogir akpe̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ asu̠wo̠ ogir\x - \xo 5:18 \xt A̠luk 10:7\x* d̠o̠yo̠.”
\p 
\v 19 Ko o̠nagha ma̠ iku ola̠ uler ugboloma̠ ma̠ okei-o̠ni̠, a̠ten ka̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠ bo̠d̠o̠ i̠sar o̠ni̠ iru ra̠ i̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ onin o̠nu̠.
\v 20 Ya̠a̠, game̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ egir i̠karabh bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh eb̠la̠ ogbo, bo̠ka̠ a̠d̠igh a̠rugugu a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo.
\v 21 Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin o̠kparakpar okoroko na̠ a̠kikiom anwa d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ Akrai̠st A̠zizo̠s, na̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ i̠na na̠ aso̠n bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ igielake̠ atu̠o̠no̠m i̠to̠to̠gi̠ i̠nye̠n, ya̠a̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ abhe̠l odi a̠kpon odi a̠gurumeni.
\v 22 Ko onugia̠n o̠gbamagi̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠ruzu a̠nwunom d̠a̠ o̠so̠n ogbo a̠dila̠de, b̠o̠ka̠ anwa na̠ od̠igh aru̠gi̠an i̠karabh ipa̠n ogbo. Ya̠a̠, rughe ma̠ ado̠l d̠oyom a̠guri d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala.
\v 23 Ko o̠d̠a ma̠ amu̠m ku̠ku̠m, ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠kara a̠min d̠a̠ ebula̠ okurogh d̠oyom, na̠ rasu̠nwe̠r ya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a ma̠ obhel na̠ eten obhel na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠me̠ni̠ nyam bho̠.
\v 24 I̠karabh idi ogbo od̠i ma̠ iya̠ na̠ ologhom na̠ o̠bi̠gh geregere, sa̠ na̠ ebhin awa ka̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ ebhum ase̠. Ya̠a̠, i̠karabh idi ogbo na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m awa d̠a̠ aman.
\v 25 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, ib̠eb̠i ogir na̠ e̠ro̠ geregere. Ya̠a̠, ib̠eb̠i ogir ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠ eka̠, ko orue d̠o̠ o̠wo̠gi̠.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ aru̠bana eloghom ma̠a̠ akpe̠ awa ma̠ ozuruna̠ eghoi onigha̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ awa bho̠. O̠ku̠a ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ko ofugh d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠i̠yar.
\v 2 Aru̠bana ya̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ awa bho̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠a̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠, okpon d̠o̠ awa e̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠, ezin bho̠ awa a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠awa. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ awa egir epeleni enigha̠ awa, ezin bho̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ asu̠wo̠ ogir d̠awa bho̠ bha̠ ogbo etula̠n ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ onin ima̠ra̠ ologi bho̠.
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ Igunugha̠ // na̠ A̠ga̠i E̠li̠la
\p Tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ma̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠awa ma̠ ogir o̠ku̠a.
\v 3 O̠ni̠ ola̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ opa̠n abar ola̠ a̠nwegia̠n na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igielake̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ a̠ga̠i ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠i̠yar,
\v 4 bha̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ agaga na̠ abu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu, sa̠ ologhom d̠o̠ bebina̠ abar. I̠na a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ i̠karabh ebhiroma̠ o̠ku̠anan kabar kabar ola̠ ufugh usoroni. Sa̠ obha̠ na̠ a̠mutiom a̠gbokia̠n, na̠ elobhiri, na̠ a̠fugh i̠te̠i̠, na̠ igurumia̠n ologi,
\v 5 na̠ iwia̠n d̠a̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ i̠karabh rologi ya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠. Awa ibhin ma̠a̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠a̠ eten o̠wo̠l ogbo e̠li̠la.
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, ado̠l igielake̠ na̠ orugh agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ni̠ ate̠i̠ ta̠ elegha̠n o̠ni̠, na̠ ebhin ibom asu̠o̠ na̠ eruom o̠ni̠.
\v 7 Abar ola̠ i̠yar ubhin uru d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon bo̠, sa̠ bebina̠ abar ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ orue obhin o̠d̠u̠a bo̠.
\v 8 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ku̠gba ma̠ i̠yar o̠te̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n od̠e na̠ ibura̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an ma̠ i̠se̠n, bha̠ i̠nye̠n elegha̠n i̠yar.
\v 9 Ya̠a̠, a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh ogbo e̠li̠la na̠ emel na̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ ad̠agi̠an, na̠ akpati̠an, na̠ a̠d̠izo i̠karabh i̠walama ibhobho i̠kpo̠ ya̠ a̠d̠ugh, ya̠ ta̠ orobh awa od̠ighom d̠a̠ egbika̠ okunugi awa.
\v 10 Ezin bho̠ otula̠n okpoki na̠ a̠mutiom eb̠la̠ i̠karabh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar. Idi ogbo d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ na̠ ewia̠n o̠te̠i̠ bho̠, na̠ ebhe d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠ ka̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ ibom i̠ku̠nu̠.
\s1 Ekunuguma̠ A̠kikiom bho̠
\p 
\v 11 Ya̠a̠, anwa A̠timoti o̠ni̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ghele ma̠ o̠kpo̠ i̠ye̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, wia̠ne ma̠ a̠rugh ado̠l igielake̠, na̠ a̠ghud̠um oghila̠n A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ ologi ima̠ra̠, na̠ etula̠n, na̠ a̠ma̠ne, na̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu.
\v 12 Wia̠ne ma̠ ibom d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠ ma̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhelegi nyam ra̠ a̠d̠ighom bho̠, wa̠ anwa i̠gba imutuma̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠d̠izo ogbo ma̠ anwa ta̠ atu̠o̠no̠m bho̠.
\v 13 Ami̠ na̠ a̠ruom anwa d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar, na̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st wa̠ amara d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Apo̠nti̠o̠s Apai̠let agba ma̠ iya̠gia̠ga̠i a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,
\v 14 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠nagha o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ oloko bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ u̠pi̠e̠ nyam, o̠li̠o̠m d̠o̠ nyam, tu̠tu̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru,
\v 15 d̠a̠ a̠ga̠i obhel wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ itutumeni bho̠, wa̠ i̠na ku̠ku̠m aro̠ ma̠ Wirileghom bho̠, na̠ O̠li̠le̠ma ta̠ Aru̠li̠le̠ma bho̠, na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ bho̠, ta̠ ato̠ bho̠.
\v 16 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, i̠na ku̠ku̠m ola̠ ko omugh d̠o̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ esi e̠b̠alab̠al ola̠ o̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠tua̠n. O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ abi̠gh i̠na bo̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue abi̠gh i̠na bo̠ nyen. Edim na̠ a̠limon ya̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton na̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠, e̠ro̠ enigha̠ i̠na. Aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a.
\v 17 Ghaghana ma̠ ogbo ya̠ igbo ma̠ e̠li̠la d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar e̠mara̠nwunom onon bho̠ ma̠a̠, awa o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu bo̠d̠o̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠li̠la ya̠ na̠ ekpokolo eb̠em ologi. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ eb̠em ologi d̠awa aro̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ onyen ologi na̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar e̠nu̠m bho̠.
\v 18 Ggba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ egir ib̠eb̠i, egbo ma̠ ibome e̠li̠la d̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i od̠ighi i̠di̠ar, enwuna̠ ma̠ onyen ologi, e̠ne̠ghe̠ na̠ onyen ologi.
\v 19 Ka̠ awa igir o̠ku̠a bha̠ awa na̠ ekpol e̠li̠la iya̠ awa, ya̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠de̠o̠ma d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, b̠o̠ka̠ awa e̠te̠i̠ a̠ga̠i a̠ghud̠um bho̠.\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Apo̠l na̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠ ma̠a̠, ogir ib̠eb̠i na̠ a̠bhin itenemeni e̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠ru. A̠kikiom bho̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ itenemeni d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh.\f*
\v 20 O A̠timoti, mare̠ ma̠ a̠sibh abar wa̠ ub̠eton u̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom bho̠. Ko o̠nagha ma̠ ibhelebhel a̠fugh, bo̠d̠o̠, i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an na̠ aku̠anan ya̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi ya̠ idi ogbo na̠ ekue na̠ ebhelegi ma̠ “eloghomabar.”
\v 21 Idi ogbo na̠ ebhin e̠re̠ma ma̠ ola̠ na̠ emel e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠.
\p E̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ inyin.
